1. clone grub-btrfs and run "make install"
2. edit 41_snapshots-btrfs (from su) and change row 72 from:
   grub_directory=${GRUB_BTRFS_GRUB_DIRNAME:-"/boot/grub"}
   to: grub_directory=${GRUB_BTRFS_GRUB_DIRNAME:-"/boot/grub2"}
3. edit /etc/default/grub-btrfs using custom file in .dotfiles
   (uncomment all rows with /boot/grub2
